Docs.summary: Various Objective-C methods wrappers that are used to invoke objc_msgSend.

remarks.para: All the methods in this class are low-level methods.
They provide convenience methods that are used to access Objective-C's underlying objc_msgSend functionality, which is how methods are invoked in Objective-C
In general, it is best if users use a binding generator like MonoTouch's btouch tool to generate bindings that will work with both the simulator and the device.
